<h2>Browser support</h2>

<p>Masonry v4 supports IE10+, Android 4+, Safari for iOS 5+, Firefox 16+, and Chrome 12+.</p>

<p>For IE8+ and Android 2.3 support, try <a href="http://masonry.desandro.com/v3">Masonry v3</a>.</p>

